            <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; "
              class="paragraph_style_2">About the PI</p>
            <div style="position: relative; width: 400px; ">
              <img src="../assets/shapeimg.jpg" alt=""
                style="height: 1px; left: 0px; margin-top: 1px; position:
                absolute; top: 0px; width: 515px; " />
            </div>

            <div class="text-content graphic_textbox_layout_style_default_External_602_184" style="padding: 0px; ">
              <div class="graphic_textbox_layout_style_default">
                <br />
                <p style="padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Jiayi Huang is an Assistant Professor in the
                  <a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;"
                    title="https://hkust-gz.edu.cn/academics/four-hubs/function-hub/microelectronics"
                    href="https://hkust-gz.edu.cn/academics/four-hubs/function-hub/microelectronics"
                    onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" class="class3">
                    Microelectronics Thrust
                  </a>
                  at
                  <a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;"
                    title="https://hkust-gz.edu.cn" href="https://hkust-gz.edu.cn"
                    onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" class="class3">
                    The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology (Guangzhou)</a>.
                  Prior to joining HKUST(GZ), he was a Research Scientist at Alibaba DAMO
                  Academy. He was a postdoc at UC Santa Barbara. He recieved his Ph.D. from Texas A&M Unviersity in 2020
                  and his B.Eng. from Zhejiang University in 2014. His research is mainly published in Computer
                  Architecture top venues such as ISCA, HPCA, and TC. He has interned at Tesla and worked on the memory
                  controller design of Autopilot Hardware. More information about the PI, please checkout
                  <a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;"
                    title="https://jyhuang91.github.io"
                    href="https://jyhuang91.github.io"
                    onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;"
                    class="class3">jyhuang91.github.io
                  </a>.
                </p>
                <br />
                <p style="padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_5">
                  I am committed to training the next-generation computer architects. My research group has several
                  openings for PhD students who are passionate about defining new computer architectures to solve
                  challenging computing problems. I am also open to working with Masters and undergraduate students as
                  research assistants.
                  <br />
                  <br />
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_2">
              Research Areas
            </p>
            <div style="position: relative; width: 400px; ">
              <img src="../assets/shapeimg.jpg" alt=""
                style="height: 1px; left: 0px; margin-top: 1px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 515px; " />
            </div>
            <ul TYPE="disc">
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Computer architecture and systems for deep learning
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Machine learning for computer architecture and systems
                  optimization
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Hardware-assisted computer security
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Network-on-chip, network-on-package, and datacenter
                  interconnection network
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  <span class="style_2"> Defined by YOU. </span> I encourage
                  students to explore interesting inter-disciplinary research
                  areas such as but not limited to bioinformatics and quantum
                  computing.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; "
              class="paragraph_style_2">Funding Support</p>
            <div style="position: relative; width: 400px; ">
              <img src="../assets/shapeimg.jpg" alt=""
                style="height: 1px; left: 0px; margin-top: 1px; position:
                absolute; top: 0px; width: 515px; " />
            </div>

            <div class="text-content graphic_textbox_layout_style_default_External_602_184" style="padding: 0px; ">
              <div class="graphic_textbox_layout_style_default"><br />
                <p style="padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Each PhD student would be supported with about 15k RMB per month. RA would also be supported.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <br />

            <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_2">
              Advising Philosophy
            </p>
            <div style="position: relative; width: 400px; ">
              <img src="../assets/shapeimg.jpg" alt=""
                style="height: 1px; left: 0px; margin-top: 1px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 515px; " />
            </div>
            <ul TYPE="disc">
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  The goal is to help students grow. The research group aims to provide a free atmosphere and equal
                  opportunities for effective communication, mutual learning, and student growth.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Specializing the development plan for individual students according to their background, interests,
                  and personality to achieve the best collaboration and chemstry.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  <span class="style_2">Dual Tutor Scheme:</span> besides me as the supervisor, I woud pair the student
                  with a co-supervisor either from a top-notch university or industry, according to the student's
                  research interest and career plan.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  My research group would provide students with opportunities for attending top conferences, oversea
                  academic exechange experience, and industry internships.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>


