                  <span class="style_2">HONEST, Curious, Self-motivated, Resilient, Hard Working, and Flexible</span>
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Strong masters and undergraduate students with background in computer science, computer engineering,
                  microelectronics, electrical engineering, VLSI, etc.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  We also welcome junior undergraduate students to participate in our projects as research assistant.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="paragraph_style_1">
                  Priority is given to applicants with research or engineering experience in computer architecture and
                  VLSI.
                </p>
